text_blocks.content: D. The final composition of the jury
Six-hundred and ninety-four potential jurors answered the 50-question questionnaire.

1 Despite attempts, defense counsel was unable to locate Juror No. 50's Twitter account at the time of voir dire because his Twitter handle (@ScottyDavidNYC) did not include his last name and may have included an inaccurate middle name.
2 The parties submitted this joint list before reviewing the second round of questionnaires.

additional_notes: The document contains redactions, likely to protect sensitive information.
